# Optional: editable install of docgen from a local clone of:
#   https://github.com/jmjava/documentation-generator
#
# Copy this file to `docgen-engine.path` (gitignored) and put ONE absolute path per line to
# the root of that clone — the directory that contains `pyproject.toml` with `name = "docgen"`.
#
# Example (replace with your machine):
#   /home/ubuntu/github/jmjava/documentation-generator
